technologies promises to revolutionize financial performance through
enhanced operational efficiencies, strategic decision-making, and
customer-centric innovations. How exactly does banking and finance AI
technology innovation influence banks’ financial performance across
global markets, and what role do economic growth and ICT development
play in shaping this relationship? Banking and finance AI technology
