(Salike & Ao, 2018). The positive and significant coefficient for the
interaction term BRAITI*GDPG indicates that the combined effect of
banking and finance AI technology innovation (BRAITI) and economic
growth on banks’ financial performance is greater than the sum of their
individual effects. This suggests that when AI technology innovation is
coupled with favorable economic growth conditions, the positive impact
on banks’ financial performance is amplified.
